item.name: Blue Slim Fit Jeans – Cliff
item.description:
The mix of authentic vintage washing and selected detailing makes it! The 'Cliff' in mid blue comes with contrasting stitching on the back pockets, seat folds on the thighs and striking white logo patch. Patched side pockets with contrasting stitching


Manufacturers product information: mid-rise slim-fit
Cut: narrow, slightly tapered legs
Measurements for size EU L32W32: waist 84 cm (33″), leg opening 34 cm (13.5″), inside leg 82 cm (32.5″), rise 24 cm (9.5″)
Waistband: belt loop and zip with snaps on the collar
Pockets: 5-pocket
Extras: distressed look with faded dyes and permanent wrinkles
Material: 98% cotton, 2% elastane
Manufacturer's care instructions: machine wash
Our model wears an EU L32W32 and is 185cm/6′0″ tall.
item.short_description: Slim fit five-pocket jeans with a washed effect. Zip fly and metal top button fastening in the front.
